=======
 FACTS 
=======
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

show some facts

| 


| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *chuck*

    :description: generate chuck norris fact

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !chuck
        <output> Chuck Norris once bet NASA he could survive re-entry
        <output>  without a spacesuit. On July 19th, 1999, a naked Chuck
        <output>  Norris re-entered the earth's atmosphere, streaking
        <output>  over 14 states and reaching a temperature of 3000
        <output>  degrees. An embarrassed NASA publically claimed it
        <output>  was a meteor, and still owes him a beer.


2) *schneier*

    :description: generate bruce schneier fact

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !schneier
        <output> The universe was created to serve as Bruce Schneier's
        <output>  crib text.


3) *theo*

    :description: generate theo de raadt fact

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !theo
        <output> It'd be one fucking happy planet if it wasn't for what's
        <output>  under this fucking sticker.


